</head>

<body>

  <div class="page-container">
    <section class="page-section">
      <h1 class="section-heading lbrxt-tscale-d4">LibRext — Shapes</h1>

      <p>Back to <a href="./index.html">Specimens</a></p>

      <p>As for shapes, LibRext deals only with boxes. There are several options available for border radius, box shadow, widget heights, and card styles</p>

      <p>Border Radius — A larger radius fits with larger boxes</p>

      <p>Box Shadow — Larger sizes imply more distance between box layer and parent layer</p>

      <p>Widget Heights — Presets for common/consistent UX elements. Like inputs, buttons, chips, etc.</p>
    </section>

    <hr class="section-divider" />

    <section class="page-section">
      <h2>Border Radii</h2>

      <p>The system has six border radius styles:</p>

      <div class="shape-box-set border-radius">
        <% for(var i=0; i < borderRadiusSizes.length; i++) { %>
        <div class="shape-box-wrapper">
          <div class="shape-box lbrxt-bradius <%= borderRadiusSizes[i].sizeCode %>">
            <span class="box-text box-heading"><%= borderRadiusSizes[i].heading %></span><br />
            <span class="box-text box-body"><%= borderRadiusSizes[i].body %></span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <% } %>
      </div>

      <hr class="section-divider page-example-divider" />

      <h2>Box Shadows</h2>

      <p>The system has five box shadow styles available:</p>

      <div class="shape-box-set box-shadow">
        <% for(var i=0; i < boxShadowSizes.length; i++) { %>
        <div class="shape-box-wrapper">
          <div class="shape-box lbrxt-b-shadow <%= boxShadowSizes[i].sizeCode %>">
            <span class="box-text box-heading"><%= boxShadowSizes[i].heading %></span><br />
            <span class="box-text box-body"><%= boxShadowSizes[i].body %></span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <% } %>
      </div>

      <hr class="section-divider page-example-divider" />

      <h2>Widgets & Inputs</h2>

      <p>The system has five available widget heights:</p>

      <div class="shape-box-set widget">
        <% for(var i=0; i < widgetSizes.length; i++) { %>
        <div class="shape-box-wrapper">
          <div class="shape-box widget lbrxt-widget <%= widgetSizes[i].sizeCode %>">
            <span class="box-text box-heading"><%= widgetSizes[i].heading %></span> —
            <span class="box-text box-body"><%= widgetSizes[i].body %></span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <% } %>
      </div>
    </section>

  </div>
  <!-- <script src="js/app.js"></script> -->

</body>

</html>